lead_paragraph: The leader of Austria's Jewish community called on a right-wing politician to drop his campaign for re-election to the European Parliament after he was quoted as likening the European Union to the Third Reich in Nazi Germany.

headline.main: Jewish Leader Raps Austrian MEP Over Third Reich Comment
headline.print_headline: Jewish Leader Raps Austrian MEP Over Third Reich Comment
